TextEng: Are you a prisoner here?
Stand back! I'll have no tricks out of you!
I'm certainly no servant of the wizard, no.
You kept in prison?
Stand back! No tricks!!
Me no servant of wizard.
How do I know you're actually a prisoner, that this isn't some ruse?
Text: 네가 정말 죄수라는 걸 어떻게 알아? 이게 속임수가 아니라고?

TextEng: I'd appreciate some information, first.
What reward would I get for letting you go?
Would you be able to find your way out on your own?
I'm not here to rescue you. Get out of my way.
Text: 난 널 구하러 온 게 아냐. 비켜.

TextEng: How I know you not lying?
Text: 너 거짓말 안 하는 거 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: Me have questions, first.
Is there reward for letting you go?
You find way out on own?
Text: 너 혼자 길 찾을 수 있어?

TextEng: Me no rescuer. Get lost.
Text: 나 구하러 온 거 아냐. 꺼져.

TextEng: I never said that. Killing you would be more fun! Ha ha ha!!
Text: 그런 말 안 했어. 널 죽이는 게 더 재밌을 것 같은데! 하 하 하!!

TextEng: Just like that. Go, I said.
I don't know. Is there anything in it for me for helping you?
Text: 모르겠군. 도와주면 내게 돌아올 게 있나?

TextEng: Me never say that! Hurting you gonna be fun! HA ha Ha!!
Text: 나 그런 말 안 했어! 너 괴롭히면 재밌어! 하하하!!

TextEng: Why not? Go, I says.
Don't know. What in it for me?
Text: 몰라. 나한테 뭐 좋은 거 있어?

TextEng: I don't trust you. Time to die!
Text: 널 믿을 수 없어. 죽을 시간이야!

TextEng: No believe! Die! Die!!
Yes, I could use some information.
You're of no use to me. Get lost.
Yes, tell me. That good.
You no use to me, then. Go.
Then go. The way behind me is clear.
Text: 그럼 가. 내 뒤쪽 길은 확보해 뒀어.

TextEng: Perhaps you should accompany me. It would be safer that way.
Text: 나와 함께 가는 게 좋겠다. 그게 더 안전해.

TextEng: Then go. Way behind is clear.
No, you come with me. Safer.
Text: 아니, 너 나랑 같이 가. 더 안전해.

TextEng: Just how did you end up prisoner here?
What do you know about this place?
All right. I'm done with you now.
How you end up in prison?
What you know of this place?
Me done with you.
But why would he keep you prisoner? A member of city guard?
Text: 하지만 그가 왜 널 가뒀지? 너는 도시 경비대원인데?

TextEng: Do you know where Meldanen could be found?
Why he keep you? You city guard.
Text: 왜 너 가뒀어? 너 도시 경비대잖아.

TextEng: Me look for Meldanen.
You're Samuel? Captain Thurin sent me to look for you.
Text: 너 사무엘이야? 투린 대장이 너 찾으라고 보냈어.

TextEng: You Samuel? Captain Thurin sends me.
Text: 너 사무엘? 투린 대장이 나 보냈어.

TextEng: Meldanen done with. Yous can go nows.
Meldanen has been taken care of. You can get out of here now.
Text: 멜다넨은 처리됐어. 이제 여기서 나갈 수 있어.
